### High Finding

#### 2. Missing Negative / Edge-Case Tests

The production code has several behavioral edges that are completely untested:

| Untested behavior | Production location | Risk |
|---|---|---|
| `UpdatePrice` on missing SKU throws `KeyNotFoundException` | Line 14 | Callers won't know if error handling works |
| `GetProduct` returns `null` for missing SKU | Line 11 | Null-reference bugs in callers |
| `ImportFromCsv` with malformed input (missing columns, bad decimal) | Lines 30-34 | Runtime `IndexOutOfRangeException` / `FormatException` in production |
| `ApplyBulkDiscount` with 0% or >100% fraction | Lines 21-24 | Potential pricing bugs (negative prices) |
| `RemoveProduct` on non-existent SKU | Line 17 | Silent no-op or exception? Behavior is unspecified |

**Fix:** Add explicit tests for each edge case:

